description: Now you can easily find out the operating status of the federal government in Washington, DC.  Just ask for Federal status and find out if your office is open.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask federal status is the government open today
Alexa, ask federal status what is the current status
name: Federal Status
shortDescription: Are you a federal government employee in Washington, DC?  Do yo want a quick answer to "is the government open today?"  Ask Federal Status and find out!
